comment: Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Leonard (SAS) on the screen.

[Observable in enhanced video] LHH shows that Leonard (SAS) hops consecutively on the same foot upon ending his dribble.
Roberson (OKC) legally contests Leonard's (SAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Westbrook (OKC) does not extend his arm into Mills (SAS) and dislodge him from his defensive position.
Gasol (SAS) sets the screen on Westbrook (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Detectable with stop watch] Aldridge (SAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen on Mills (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Aldridge (SAS) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically contesting Westbrook's (OKC) driving shot attempt. Aldridge cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Mills (SAS) attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
McDermott (OKC) makes contact to Leonard's (SAS) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Leonard (SAS) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) and Abrines (OKC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Adams (OKC) committed a take foul prior to the game clock expiring is confirmed and the game clock is reset to 00:00.6.
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on Leonard (SAS).
